  "description": "## Topology defined Line\n\n%definition% \n\nA feature type using a topology property to reference an ordered list of points.\n\nThe topology property has an ordered array, defining the direction of the line from the first to second and subsequent points.\n\nThis is a generalisation of the TopoJSON concept using inline data, and hence not limited to linestrings.\n\n",
  "examples": [
    {
      "title": "LineString",
      "snippets": [
        {
          "language": "json",
          "base-uri": "http://www.example.com/features/",
          "ref": "https://surroundaustralia.github.io/topo-feature/_sources/features/topo-line/examples/linestring.json",
          "shacl-closure": [
            "../topo-feature/examples/points.ttl"
          ],
          "url": "https://surroundaustralia.github.io/topo-feature/build/tests/geo/topo/features/topo-line/example_1_1.json",
          "code": "{\n  \"type\": \"Feature\",\n  \"id\": \"LineP1P2\",\n  \"geometry\": null,\n  \"topology\": {\n    \"type\": \"Edge\",\n    \"references\": [\n      \"P1\",\n      \"P2\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"properties\": null\n}"
        },
        {
          "language": "jsonld",
          "url": "https://surroundaustralia.github.io/topo-feature/build/tests/geo/topo/features/topo-line/example_1_1.jsonld",
          "code": "{\n  \"@context\": \"https://surroundaustralia.github.io/topo-feature/build/annotated/geo/topo/features/topo-line/context.jsonld\",\n  \"type\": \"Feature\",\n  \"id\": \"LineP1P2\",\n  \"geometry\": null,\n  \"topology\": {\n    \"type\": \"Edge\",\n    \"references\": [\n      \"P1\",\n      \"P2\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"properties\": null\n}"
        },
        {
          "language": "ttl",
          "url": "https://surroundaustralia.github.io/topo-feature/build/tests/geo/topo/features/topo-line/example_1_1.ttl",
          "code": "@prefix geojson: <https://purl.org/geojson/vocab#> .\n@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .\n@prefix topo: <https://purl.org/geojson/topo#> .\n\n<http://www.example.com/features/LineP1P2> a geojson:Feature ;\n    geojson:topology [ a topo:Edge ;\n            topo:relatedFeatures ( <http://www.example.com/features/P1> <http://www.example.com/features/P2> ) ] .\n\n"
        }
      ]
    },
